        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This <em>+3 greater striking @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Flaming (Greater)]{Greater Flaming} longsword</em> has an ornate brass hilt and a blade shaped like stylized flames. When wielded, the blade projects illumination resembling shimmering firelight, emitting dim light in a 10-foot radius.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate—Shoot Fire</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> (concentrate, manipulate)</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Ignition] cantrip from the sword as a 9th-rank arcane spell, using your melee attack modifier with <em>searing blade</em> as your spell attack modifier.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate—Radiate Flames</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">A</span> (aura, concentrate, fire)</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> A @Template[type:emanation|distance:10] of flame radiates from the <em>greater searing blade</em> for 1 minute. All weapon and unarmed attacks by you and your allies within the area gain the effect of the <em>flaming</em> property rune.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.Aura: Searing Blade (Greater)]</p>"
